Package org.framework.rodolfo.freire.git.bank.authorize.model

Class Transaction

java.lang.Object
org.framework.rodolfo.freire.git.bank.authorize.model.Transaction
@Entity public class Transaction extends Object
Model that represents a financial transaction.

The Transaction class models a transaction record, including details such as the transaction ID, associated account ID, transaction amount, merchant, Merchant Category Code (MCC), date, and time. This class is used to store and manage transaction information within the system.

The class uses JPA annotations for persistence and follows standard Java conventions for representing transaction data.
